            Phir story mein twist aata hai jab hosts self-aware ho jate hain aur humans aur machines ke darmiyan control aur survival ki struggle start ho jati hai.

            <br /><br />

            Yeh series consciousness, free will, aur human vs AI ke concept ko explore karti hai.

